Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: 1988 televised debates, and Thatcher in 1979
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p00ydsb7
Last Broadcast Date: Fri 7 Oct 1988
The polished nature of the Bush/Dukakis debates, the 'American-style' of Margaret Thatcher's public relations in 1979, and Jimmy Carter's negative review of the 1988 campaign.